+# Cursor Contract
+
+Cursor should behave like a fast local editor for Pala:
+- prefer shallow context
+- keep files focused
+- make the visible UI crisp and readable
+- avoid broad rewrites unless the surface is explicitly changing
+
+## Best use
+- iterating on a component or page
+- reshaping a single workflow
+- polishing dashboard copy and layout
+
+## Guardrails
+- keep evidence in the ledger
+- do not invent a green state
+- route source imports through source cards
