+# Pala OS V6 Local Boot
+
+Status: `RELEASE_BLOCKED`
+
+Bu belge local-first boot artefact'larinin ne sagladigini yazar.
+
+## Available Local Boot Surfaces
+
+- dashboard runtime:
+  - `node src/cli.js up`
+  - `npm run start`
+- MCP read runtime:
+  - `node src/cli.js mcp serve`
+  - `npm run mcp:serve`
+- Docker local boot:
+  - `docker compose up pala-v6-dashboard`
+  - `docker compose up pala-v6-mcp`
+  - `node src/cli.js docker smoke`
+
+## Constraints
+
+- bu artefact'lar deploy artefact degil
+- production hardening yok
+- owner approval gerektiren hareketler serbest degil
+- default court state hala `RELEASE_BLOCKED`
+
+## Honest Gaps
+
+- compose smoke sadece `docker compose config` ve service resolution seviyesinde
+- container build/up smoke bu makinede henuz kosulmadi
+- host plugin install flow baglanmadi
+- benchmark runner compose'e entegre degil
+- GitHub read-only env wiring compose icinde yok
