+# Pala OS V6 Minimum MCP Spec
+
+Status: `RELEASE_BLOCKED`
+
+Bu belge uygulama degil. Read-only audit sonucunda, V6'nin ilk gercek MCP katmani icin minimum spesifikasyonu tanimlar.
+
+## Purpose
+
+V6 icin MCP katmaninin amaci:
+
+- Codex'in yerine gecmek degil
+- Codex ustunde calisan control-tower katmanina:
+  - tool health
+  - skill discovery
+  - court-safe read surfaces
+  - allowlist disiplini
+  saglamak
+
+## Required Constraints
+
+- Local-first
+- Read-heavy by default
+- Destructive ops forbidden by default
+- Owner approval olmadan:
+  - GitHub write
+  - Slack send
+  - deploy
+  - release
+  - source import
+  yok
+- Telemetry content-free olmali; tool name, event type, duration gibi minimal veri yeterli
+
+## Minimum Tool Set
+
+V1 icin alinacak minimum MCP tool kontrati:
+
+1. `pala_list_skills`
+2. `pala_get_skill`
+3. `pala_search_skills`
+4. `pala_health`
+
+Bilerek disarida birakilan:
+
+- `pala_recommend`
+  Not:
+  - lineage repo'da degerli
+  - ama V6 read-only bootstrap fazinda zorunlu degil
+  - premium/network/licensing semantics getirdigi icin ikinci faza kalabilir
+
+## Health Contract
+
+`pala_health` en az su sinyalleri donmeli:
+
+- registry exists
+- registry parse ok
+- skills root reachable
+- source-court rule file reachable
+- ledger reachable
+- dashboard state reachable
+- blocked release state
+
+Saglik PASS olsa bile:
+
+- court hala `RELEASE_BLOCKED` olabilir
+- health = runtime alive
+- release = governance cleared
+
+## Permission Budget
+
+Minimum permission modeli:
+
+- filesystem: read-only
+- network: allowlist-only veya off by default
+- shell: forbidden from MCP tool side
+- secrets: forbidden
+- destructive_ops: forbidden
+
+## V6-Specific Evidence Hooks
+
+Her MCP related event idealde su kayitlardan en az birine dusmeli:
+
+- `events`
+- `tool_usage`
+- `gate_decisions`
+
+V6 DB'de bunlar zaten var; MCP spec bu yuzden bu tablolara dogal oturuyor.
+
+## API / Runtime Relationship
+
+MCP server truth ureten katman degil.
+
+Truth kaynaklari:
+
+- SQLite
+- JSONL ledger
+- source cards
+- standards
+- gate decisions
+
+MCP bunlari:
+
+- bulur
+- arar
+- okur
+- saglik raporlar
+
+## Quarantine Rules
+
+Asagidaki seyler minimum MCP spec disinda kalir:
+
+- deploy-ready compose reuse
+- cloud HTTP gateway
+- production auth packaging
+- premium billing/licensing semantics
+- public plugin packaging
+
+## Acceptance for Future Build Phase
+
+Ileride build fazina gecildiginde minimum MCP spec icin aranacak kanit:
+
+1. local process boot ediyor
+2. `pala_health` DB/registry/ledger visibility raporluyor
+3. tool set sadece allowlist icindeki read tools ile basliyor
+4. tool calls ledger/tool_usage izine baglaniyor
+5. court state `RELEASE_BLOCKED` olarak korunuyor
+
+## Evidence Basis
+
+- `docs/inheritance-backlog.json`
+- `docs/v6-readonly-audit-report.md`
+- `pala-os/mcp-server/README.md`
+- `pala-os/mcp-server/plugin.json`
+- `pala-os/mcp-server/src/pala_mcp/server.py`
