+# OSS Upstream Matrix
+
+Pala OS V6 cekirdegi local-first kalir. Dis kaynaklar cekirdege dogrudan baglanmaz; source card, adapter siniri ve lisans kontrolu olmadan hicbiri "core truth" olmaz.
+
+## Doctrine
+
+- `MIT-first` ya da acik ve dusuk-riskli lisans tercih edilir.
+- Her subsystem icin `1 primary` ve en fazla `1 fallback` upstream secilir.
+- Koddan once desen ve operasyon mantigi alinır.
+- "Cool project" ile "core dependency" ayni sey degildir.
+- Pala'nin DB + ledger + court + no-fake-done hukuku korunur.
+
+## Primary Reference Matrix
+
+| Reference | License / note | Layer | Decision | What we take |
+| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
+| OpenHands | Core repo MIT, `enterprise/` ayri lisansli | mission control, orchestration, agent surfaces | `ADOPT_PATTERN` | multi-surface agent platform, secure sandbox posture, GitHub/Slack/API delegation, auditable runs, CLI + SDK + UI fikri |
+| UI/UX Pro Max | MIT | dashboard visual doctrine | `ADOPT_PATTERN` | analytics dashboard styles, typography discipline, stronger visual intent, style/UX reasoning, dashboard bilgi mimarisi |
+| Continue | Apache-2.0 | repo-native checks and CI gates | `ADAPT_PATTERN` | `.agents` / `.continue` check mantigi, PR status checks, source-controlled agent prompts |
+| Cline | Apache-2.0 | operator workflow surface | `ADAPT_PATTERN` | CLI + IDE + kanban dusuncesi, parallel task board, human-in-the-loop approval |
+| Aider | Apache-2.0 | terminal discipline | `ADAPT_PATTERN` | repo-aware terminal loop, pragmatic git-first operation, low-ceremony repair flow |
+
+## Pala Mapping
+
+### OpenHands -> Pala
+
+- Dashboard'i sadece "metrics page" degil, gorev + court + source + jobs + bridge yuzeyi olarak dusundurur.
+- Tek bir arayuz yerine `CLI + dashboard + local API` uclusu kullanmamizi destekler.
+- GitHub ve ileride Slack gibi ortamlari "delegation surface" olarak gormemizi saglar.
+- Pala farki: bizde agent'in ustunde court ve ledger hukuku daha serttir.
+
+### UI/UX Pro Max -> Pala
+
+- Dashboard'in sade admin panel gibi kalmamasini zorlar.
+- Typography, hierarchy ve analytics-style layout kararlarini daha bilincli verir.
+- Pala farki: biz skill'i degil, onun urun seviyesi gorsel disiplinini kendi command-radar dilimize ceviririz.
+
+### Continue -> Pala
+
+- Repo icinde makine-okunur gate mantigini guclendirir.
+- `.agents` dizinini crosstool agent konfig standardi olarak ciddiye almamizi saglar.
+- Pala farki: Continue PR check disiplini saglar; Pala ise local court + evidence hafizasi ekler.
+
+### Cline -> Pala
+
+- Tek agent yerine operasyon tahtasi dusuncesi getirir.
+- Headless, CLI ve approval surface'lerini ayni urunde birlestirme fikrini guclendirir.
+- Pala farki: kanban ya da multi-agent gozukse bile ana truth gene DB + ledger olur.
+
+### Aider -> Pala
+
+- Terminal deneyimini fazla agirmadan etkili tutma dersi verir.
+- Git ve repo context'ini aktif calisma araci yapar.
+- Pala farki: Aider hizlidir; Pala o hizin ustune audit ve court bindirir.
+
+## Current Local Stack
+
+- Node 24 built-in `node:sqlite` -> local DB
+- built-in `fetch` -> read-only GitHub bridge
+- built-in HTTP server -> dashboard and read-only API
+
+## Immediate Adoption Plan
+
+1. OpenHands'ten:
+   - dashboard bilgi mimarisi
+   - multi-surface operation hissi
+   - auditable run dili
+2. UI/UX Pro Max'ten:
+   - dashboard visual hierarchy
+   - stronger analytics / control room aesthetics
+   - more deliberate typography and panel rhythm
+3. Continue'dan:
+   - `.agents` check/gate modeli
+   - repo-native policy prompts
+4. Cline + Aider'dan:
+   - terminal, CLI, approval ve run ergonomisi
+
+## Boundaries
+
+- Legacy repo kodu dogrudan import edilmez.
+- Dis UI kit'ler cekirdege baglanmadan once source card alir.
+- Lisansi belirsiz ya da yuksek bagimlilikli upstream "reference only" kalir.
+- Pala OS V6'nin command law'i:
+  - ledger bosse yesil yok
+  - owner approval yoksa release yok
+  - source card yoksa import yok
